nodes.text: Zingo Gabnit was a bounty hunter who operated in the Outer Rim Territories during the Imperial Era and was a known associate of the Xan sisters. He collaborated with the Rebel Alliance, killing several Bounty Hunters' Guild members who were pursuing rebels. On the planet Carajam, Boba Fett encountered Gabnit, taking a job to kill him shortly afterward.
